This image is an organizational chart representing the structure and roles within a research lab.    The structure shows a centralized hierarchy where all roles report directly to "Your Lab".  The Director is identified as the owner of the organization.  Key roles include a Lab Manager, PhD Student, Research Assistant, and Post-Doc, all classified as members. 


